    "This is due to content spreading in private networks, such as closed Facebook groups and chats on messaging apps like WhatsApp, as well as being sent by nefarious political actors clearly interested in using GenAI tools covertly [125].The vast majority (80%) of countries evidently experienced GenAI usage during their national elections in 2024.",
